      <title>拜登在南卡罗来纳州民主党初选中轻松获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/biden-easily-wins-south-carolina-s-democratic-primary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统在南卡罗来纳州民主党初选中轻松获胜，这次投票考验了他在黑人选民和独立人士中的支持率——并将影响妮基·黑莉在三周内击败唐纳德·特朗普在共和党竞选中的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/biden-easily-wins-south-carolina-s-democratic-primary</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 00:27:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
